---
---

<section id="como-funciona" class="bg-[#1e3d5f] py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-14 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Cómo funciona</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 font-body max-w-lg mx-auto text-base">
        Tres pasos simples para descubrir tu afinidad electoral.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="bg-white/[0.08] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 group hover:bg-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-2xl">edit_note</span>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">arrow_outward</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">Responde el test</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Marca tu postura en los temas que hoy mejor separan a las candidaturas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white/[0.08] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 group hover:bg-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-2xl">groups</span>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">arrow_outward</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">Explora candidatos</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Revisa el perfil, partido y propuestas clave de cada candidatura presidencial.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white/[0.08] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 group hover:bg-white/[0.14] transition-colors">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-2xl">analytics</span>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">arrow_outward</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3">Decide con contexto</h3>
          <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Usa tu ranking de afinidad como guía rápida antes de profundizar en fuentes oficiales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
